 ingredients!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295990/extras/6946e32546d2da72f075fa0ed846230a.poster.avif?t=1731349813\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295990/extras/6946e32546d2da72f075fa0ed846230a.webm?t=1731349813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295990/extras/6946e32546d2da72f075fa0ed846230a.mp4?t=1731349813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295990/extras/ba1dad42b00b6b9efb38d5902d812150.poster.avif?t=1731349813\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295990/extras/ba1dad42b00b6b9efb38d5902d812150.webm?t=1731349813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295990/extras/ba1dad42b00b6b9efb38d5902d812150.mp4?t=1731349813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mischievous imps will do their best to get in your way. Stop them from stealing your ingredients (and maybe throw them in the lava while you're at it).</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Finish before the time runs out!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295990/extras/4ee440c624d3a24f272ce0d7d97e93a7.avif?t=1731349813\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295990/extras_big/4ee440c624d3a24f272ce0d7d97e93a7.avif?t=1731349813 width=800 height=450 /></span>As you cook the lava will rise; submit everything before the time runs out! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If Satan's appetite isn't satisfied, who knows what he'll do!</p>",
